f=AI & Agents/scout/operational/skill/scout-skill-routing.md · h1:scout Skill Routing (no identity layer non-leader)=`cadence ─► ecosystem-scanning ─shortlist─► tool-evaluation-intake (tools) / marketplace-skill-scouting (skills) / forge (techniques) / edge (platforms) \· ▲ checks first: adopt-reject-registry \· intake verdict ─► adopt-reject-registry (record) ─adopts─► relay (register + grants) \· build starts / PENDING note ─► marketplace-skill-scouting ─► present → STOP → operator approval → meta's standards` · h1:scout Skill Routing (no identity layer non-leader)=Handoffs out: relay (registration) aegis (security judgment) forge (technique candidates) edge (platform candidates) operator (every adoption approval) quinn (sandbox trials). Precedence: registry check expiring verdicts solicited searches cadence scans.